test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -1 == -18
 +  where -1 = <built-in function prod>([-1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (1 == 3)
 +  where 1 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x74a21b97ce40>([-18])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x74a21b97ce40> = [[1], [1, -18], [1, -18, 1], [1, -18, 1, -18], [1, -18, 1, -18, 1], [1, -18, 1, -18, 1, -18], ...].count
